{
  "stem": "16345.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were many, many Jewish people in-- in Przytyk who did not speak much of the Polish language [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which is actually amazing to-- when you think about it now.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my-- both my parents and grandparents spoke Polish like natives, which they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish, mostly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also-- they used to get Polish, and they used to get some German stations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was a crystal set.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how far those things reach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember I-- I once listened-- I once listened to a Polish minister make a speech.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, we'll never give in to Germany, because Germany wanted a part of Poland before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will never give in to what the Germans want.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it didn't take them long to back down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some of the memories that stand out are when [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we would-- when the Germans were attacking Poland, we went to a farm.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our whole family went to a-- a farm of-- that a-- a gentile friend of ours owned.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed there for about a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By that time, the war was over and the Germans were-- had taken Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of my first memories was the Germans were taking collaborators.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had collaborators, Polish people who helped them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my grandfather, who was pretty old as far as I was concerned-- he was probably in his 50's.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a-- a beard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most religious people wore the religious garb, like a black-- a black frock coat, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember they-- they-- they needed some work done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Either they-- they claimed they wanted some work done.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
